&lt;h2&gt;THE WORK&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Ripple intern, you will work on challenges that impact our mission and shape our company. With support from your team, access to learning and development resources, and opportunities for fun along the way, our program will give you the foundation to start your career journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Sales intern will support the Ripple Payments and Ripple Custody Sales teams to build a robust pool of potential customers this summer. They will play a crucial role at the company, qualifying leads to identify viable sales opportunities for our sales pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will be responsible for developing strategy, sourcing and securing strategic relationships with crypto friendly payment companies, FinTech, banks to deliver Ripple’s vision, launch new products/verticals and drive network outcome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We take an inclusive approach to the market and expect to partner with all types of financial institutions, including financial technology (FinTech) companies. Your responsibility will be to map this market, prioritize prospects, and source partnerships. You will play a crucial role at the company, qualifying leads to identify viable sales opportunities for our sales pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/h2&gt;
