&lt;li&gt;Conduct industry and market research to identify key market opportunities and optimize the team’s sales effort&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source prospective Ripple partners including payment and FinTech companies, financial institutions and digital asset infrastructure players, and tech companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the sourcing of new deals by searching for opportunities on major platforms, databases, attending conferences, meetups, among others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships with cross-functional teams; collaborate with compliance, legal, and finance to ensure efficient and compliant strategy execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spot opportunities through structured qualitative customer feedback, quantitative analyses, and competitive analyses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the “voice of the market” through industry research, competitive analysis, quantitative analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
